<HEADLINE>
FT  11 APR 94 / Cows step out in designer boots
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A company which makes wellington boots has created a designer boot for cows.
The Gates Rubber Company, in Dumfries, is working flat out to meet demand
from farmers all over the country.
Hobbleboots cost Pounds 18 each and have been created to help the huge
number of cattle which developed foot rot this winter.
