business inventories (February). International Energy Agency holds seminar
in Kyoto. Mr George Bush, former US president, visits Singapore to deliver a
keynote address at a Citibank seminar on 'opportunities and obstacles facing
the region this decade and beyond' at the National University of Singapore.
Bundesbank council meets.
