Black &amp; Edgington, the USM-quoted group which provides portable buildings,
tents and other structures for sporting occasions and exhibitions, reported
a pre-tax deficit of Pounds 1.2m for the six months to January 31 1994.
The outcome was struck on turnover of Pounds 2.21m and compared with a
